{"title":"centos 配置","date":"2014-06-28T09:05:00.000Z","link":"centos-network-setting-in-vertual-box","comments":true,"tags":["tools"],"categories":["代码"],"updated":"2020-04-15T21:36:20.851Z","content":"<p>要配一个 vagrant box 给同事用。</p>\n<h3 id=\"下面是配置过程\">下面是配置过程<a href=\"centos-network-setting-in-vertual-box#下面是配置过程\"></a></h3><ol>\n<li><p>在 centos 官网下了 minimal 的版本。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>在 virtual 中安装，一切顺利。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>安装好后没有网络，启用网络</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>修改文件<code>/etc/sysconfig/network-scripts/ifcfg-eth0:</code></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">ONBOOT</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"yes\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">NM_CONTROLLED</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"no\"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>重启后就有网络了。</p>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>下一步切换 yum 源</li>\n</ol>\n<p>mv /etc/yum.repos.d/CentOS-Base.repo /etc/yum.repos.d/CentOS-Base.repo.backup</p>\n<p>minimal 版本没有 wget，所以用 curl</p>\n<p>curl -o <a href=\"http://mirrors.163.com/.help/CentOS6-Base-163.repo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">http://mirrors.163.com/.help/CentOS6-Base-163.repo</a> /etc/yum.repos.d/CentOS6-Base-163.repo</p>\n<ol start=\"5\">\n<li>生成 yum 源缓存：<br>yum makecache</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"参考链接\">参考链接<a href=\"centos-network-setting-in-vertual-box#参考链接\"></a></h3><p><a href=\"http://mirrors.163.com/.help/centos.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">http://mirrors.163.com/.help/centos.html</a></p>\n","prev":{"title":"AbstractWorker","link":"docs-javascript-MDN-classes-2014-08-11-AbstractWorker"},"next":{"title":"angular 一步一个坑","link":"angular-一步一个坑"},"plink":"https://wuwb.github.io/centos-network-setting-in-vertual-box/","reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"吴文斌","link":"<a href=\"https://wuwb.github.io/centos-network-setting-in-vertual-box/\" title=\"centos 配置\">https://wuwb.github.io/centos-network-setting-in-vertual-box/</a>","license":"自由转载-非商用-禁止演绎-保持署名 (<a href=\\\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0/\\\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)"}}